Title: Non-diagonal solutions to reflection equations in $su(n)$ spin chains

Authors: J. Abad and M.Rios

Comments: 9 pages, PlainTex , two figures uuencoded, Harvmac.

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B352 (1995) 92-95

The reflection equations in a $su(3)$ spin chain with open boundary conditionsare analyzed. We find non diagonal solutions to the boundary matrices. Thecorresponding hamiltonian is given. The solutions are generalized to $su(n)$.